I &lt;3 quote tags. Also, no; changing charm so that snare does not apply to a broken pet is unquestionably a nerf of charm, and not of snare. Cleric / pally stun is something the character does at the time of charm break, just like everything else (running away, WoM, etc). Snare is unique in that it keeps the enchanter safe and is applied continuiously. Also, this is not a discussion thread. It is to provide ideas, and (maybe) supporting ideas. 
