                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I love to Charm alot. It's what really made me love this class. I would play enchanter anway, but love is better than all the others. I've found DPS with Charm Pets while in a group and the charm breaks is PITA. I've found DC Charm Pets while in a group with shammy/bst buffs to be great for everyone. Most groups will play in a wonderful supporting fashion knowing that everyone is doing their roles(roleplay game). I've never believed the Chanter Pet to be a Main Tank for a group, but then some people don't really like groups. To make up for the loss of DC pet we now have AA for controlling our summoned pet. The benefit of having a Charmed Pet for chanters was having the control pet abilities. 
